WfPUhrPhEmlw&oe=67407469"}, {"file_name": "screenshot5.png", "id": "8845337365511342", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974827_8845337368844675_8124596110776963855_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uBCxpabs6mQQ7kNvgF5P8id&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBoPwiJ-3P5FAvB6xi0B3X1Em7hKysKMNiRYohhR4CaBQ&oe=67407CFA"}, {"file_name": "screenshot4.png", "id": "493652826753271", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982669_493652830086604_1356591045350723914_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CtAuXRYYLFEQ7kNvgHOrIqN&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBefDqLYSx5lVedKKiuoQK7Ef94q7kQXbE--C2VSXCfDA&oe=67405DAF"}, {"file_name": "screenshot3.png", "id": "1975791286174874", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75617316_1975791289508207_3268933886255417075_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QZav0X1yVGYQ7kNvgHFe52s&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBXDm72BfuPqaiyoydk464CA9osU19rP7siTDrp3Ga7PQ&oe=67407785"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Halloween Treat Rescue", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# About\n\nGrab your pickle guns, climb on top of your candy-vacuuming, self-driving chariot, and clean the village of the candy-stealing creeps which have taken control! Take back insane amounts of candy, duck the slimy stuff the creeps throw at you, and battle your way to the final boss to claim Halloween back from the creeps!\n\nHalloween: Treat Rescue is your perfect family-friendly, decidedly non-scary, silly party game. It's halloweeny, full of pumpkins, ghosts, skeletons, and candy, challenging, and just plain fun!\n\n# Levels, Difficulty, Points\n\nBattle your way through seven levels in four difficulty settings. Collect candy for points and to use it for refilling your health, and build up a shield. Don't trigger a sugar overload - sugar is bad for you!\n\nYou will also be rated on accuracy as well as how much candy you manage to dispose of during gameplay... and by dispose of, we mean EAT IT!\n\n# How to play\n\nPlay seated or standing - you'll use your controllers to shoot as well as eat the candy. \n\nThe game auto-adjusts to any height of the player.\n\nFour difficulty levels ranging from Easy to Insane mean everyone can play, and finish, this game. ", "short_description": "Grab your pickle guns, climb on top of your candy-vacuuming, self-driving chariot, and defeat the creeplings to take back your treats! And, well, the village too."}]}, "developer_name": "Sourcenity", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sourcenity.com/privacypolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Sourcenity", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.sourcenity.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [{"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8605541859478465"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1109495567439761"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "847563994180594"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "847563994180594"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1734372000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1109495567439761"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "